list.title: ArrayManager.contains

list.title: CommandManager.getArguments
list.description: Gets the arguments entered by the sender

list.description: Gets the name of the command.

list.description: Registers a new command with the specified parameters. If a command with the same name already exists, it updates its permission and callback, otherwise, it adds a new command to the list.

list.description: Translates alternate color codes in the given string to their corresponding ChatColor codes.
